      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not even about a new perspective. it's just... the weight of it. the debt, the embarrassment, the way everyone's gonna look at me. it's like a physical pressure in my chest. i'm just so tired of fighting to keep my head above water when there's nothing left to hold onto. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise is to just let go.",
